OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and bright with a light
OL,6,Fbreeze. Plenty of hazy sunshine and
OL,7,Fsunny spells at times. Another hot
OL,8,Fday, though perhaps a little cooler
OL,9,Fwhere sea breezes develop near the
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FPerhaps a little more cloud
OL,13,Fnear the coast but long clear spells
OL,14,Fare expected inland. Light winds
OL,15,Fallowing the odd mist patch to form.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FVariable amounts of cloud
OL,18,Fthrough the morning but turning
OL,19,Fbrighter through the afternoon,
OL,20,Fespecially further south and west
OL,21,Fwhere it will be hot. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
